                <note rend="inline" type="source">891.51A/377: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Persia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Philip</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-08-02T17:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 2, 1927—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>37. Having in view events reported in Legation’s 50, July 30, 5 p.m., Department
                    instructs you to say to Persian Government, provided there should appear to you
                    no ground for objection, that the American Government, recalling the help which
                    it gave unofficially at instance of Persian Government in selection of financial
                    advisers, has now decided to reserve entire liberty in acting upon future
                    requests which it may receive for assistance in promoting the engagement of its
                    nationals as advisers to Persian Government. It should be made quite plain to
                    the Persian Government that the Government of the United States would not wish
                    its relations with the American advisers since 1922 to be used hereafter and
                    under altered conditions as a binding precedent.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
